Z_jG36QwkU_UvRcAQbT0VM=/1536x1022/02644afe-3806-4459-83fb-bccdde280985--2024-1011_frieling_double-walled-french-press-and-gwp-frother_butter_mid_email-site_mj-kroeger_228.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/Z1RuNBmrISBD5pVpCwzQof3TDOY=/375x250/filters:format(webp)/02644afe-3806-4459-83fb-bccdde280985--2024-1011_frieling_double-walled-french-press-and-gwp-frother_butter_mid_email-site_mj-kroeger_228.jpg, https://images.food52.com/h4TyZRVoL1LiWUTtAU7DDHsx6gg=/750x500/filters:format(webp)/02644afe-3806-4459-83fb-bccdde280985--2024-1011_frieling_double-walled-french-press-and-gwp-frother_butter_mid_email-site_mj-kroeger_228.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/Iyb97BGU_vyGb2POo9eF0ir20F8=/375x250/02644afe-3806-4459-83fb-bccdde280985--2024-1011_frieling_double-walled-french-press-and-gwp-frother_butter_mid_email-site_mj-kroeger_228.jpg, https://images.food52.com/cjpYtBYs6PdXfc4sCNyB0nWLL24=/750x500/02644afe-3806-4459-83fb-bccdde280985--2024-1011_frieling_double-walled-french-press-and-gwp-frother_butter_mid_email-site_mj-kroeger_228.jpg 2x\" alt=\"french press and two coffees\" width=\"1348\" height=\"898\" data-pin-media=\"https://images.food52.com/WUTiHg-VNyXy6ywaUvakcoEjhNU=/2000x2000/02644afe-3806-4459-83fb-bccdde280985--2024-1011_frieling_double-walled-french-press-and-gwp-frother_butter_mid_email-site_mj-kroeger_228.jpg\" data-pin-url=\"https://food52.com/blog/28612-come-on-over-hosting-burnout\" data-pin-description=\"6 Hosting Tips for When You Don’t Feel Like Hosting on Food52\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/Iyb97BGU_vyGb2POo9eF0ir20F8=/375x250/02644afe-3806-4459-83fb-bccdde280985--2024-1011_frieling_double-walled-french-press-and-gwp-frother_butter_mid_email-site_mj-kroeger_228.jpg, https://images.food52.com/cjpYtBYs6PdXfc4sCNyB0nWLL24=/750x500/02644afe-3806-4459-83fb-bccdde280985--2024-1011_frieling_double-walled-french-press-and-gwp-frother_butter_mid_email-site_mj-kroeger_228.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://images.food52.com/WUTiHg-VNyXy6ywaUvakcoEjhNU=/2000x2000/02644afe-3806-4459-83fb-bccdde280985--2024-1011_frieling_double-walled-french-press-and-gwp-frother_butter_mid_email-site_mj-kroeger_228.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePhoto by MJ Kroeger\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/section\u003e\n\n\n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n          \u003cdiv\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eWelcome to the latest edition of Come On Over, Food52 editorial director Julie Vadnal\u0026#39;s newsletter that\u0026#39;s all about hosting gatherings big and small—without losing your cool. Got company? \u003ca href=\"https://food52.attn.tv/p/HBo/comeonover\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSign up here\u003c/a\u003e for her emails.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003chr/\u003e\n\n              \u003cp\u003eIt’s been a long year, right? And I sincerely hope you’re getting a much-deserved break from hosting. But also—these lazy days sandwiched between two holidays always seem to be the time when neighbors, family, and friends pop by to say hello. What do you do when the doorbell rings and you’re still in your pajamas at 3 p.m.? Here’s how I host when I don’t really feel like hosting.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n              \u003cp\u003eIt’s easy to get self-conscious about your home, your outfit, your hair—but remember that they’re here to see you, and no one expects a lot this time of year. Throwing on this \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/13368-house-no-23-alaia-sherpa-robe\"\u003ecozy robe\u003c/a\u003e  always makes me feel more put together, though.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003ca data-vendor-id=\"1019\" data-vendor-name=\"House no. 23\" data-category-name=\"Bath Towels \u0026amp; Accessories\" data-price=\"198.0\" data-g