b-9b5ed5b1bf41--2024-1108_house-no-23_sherpa-robe_indigo_mid_email-site_1x1_mark-weinberg_0117.jpg\" data-pin-url=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/13368-house-no-23-alaia-sherpa-robe\" data-pin-description=\"Sherpa Robeon Food52\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/mNbHo3Ei20eEFjI9B73TN5-DdL8=/470x470/2d4b0813-0acd-415a-888b-9b5ed5b1bf41--2024-1108_house-no-23_sherpa-robe_indigo_mid_email-site_1x1_mark-weinberg_0117.jpg, https://images.food52.com/bFZN47858wgStu_X1eCHY9DGWIU=/940x940/2d4b0813-0acd-415a-888b-9b5ed5b1bf41--2024-1108_house-no-23_sherpa-robe_indigo_mid_email-site_1x1_mark-weinberg_0117.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://images.food52.com/hFStkFKQj4hm7bAmvpZEt3zno-E=/1000x1000/2d4b0813-0acd-415a-888b-9b5ed5b1bf41--2024-1108_house-no-23_sherpa-robe_indigo_mid_email-site_1x1_mark-weinberg_0117.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/a\u003e\n      \n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n              \n              \u003cp\u003eYour pop-in visitors might even bring gifts. (What monsters!) That’s why I keep a box of \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/9104-plant-the-box-scented-candles\"\u003escented candles\u003c/a\u003e—I personally think candles are great gifts—and ribbons in my home office. That way, when I get the “We’re in the neighborhood\u0026#34; text, I’m ready.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n  \n\n\n              \n              \u003cp\u003eMy family keeps all our Christmas cookies in tins by type. Take a few from each tin, arrange them on a \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/11878-mepra-original-vintage-stainless-steel-round-tray\"\u003efancy silver tray\u003c/a\u003e, and suddenly, you’re the low-effort host with the most.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n  \n\n\n\n              \n              \u003cp\u003eCoffee and cookies—who wouldn’t feel welcome with that combo? Keep your \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/421-double-walled-french-press\"\u003ebrew warm\u003c/a\u003e while you all laze in the living ro